Instructions to check out login functionalities:
1)install XAMPP
2)Copy quiz folder to C:/xampp/htdocs
3)Start Apache and MySQL servers from XAMPP control panel
4)Go to http://localhost/phpMyAdmin and create database dbtest
5)execute query for table creation given in tbl_users in SQL tab
6)open url: http://localhost/quiz

Your mission should you choose to accept:
1)Improve the pages/themes
2)Learn to use bootstrap and improve pages using that
